Package GUI

Class MesonetFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Window
          • java.awt.Frame
            • javax.swing.JFrame
              • GUI.MesonetFrame

  • public class MesonetFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Mesonet Frame class holds all of the panels and has the ability to open files, calculate different parts of the file based on what check boxes are selected, and exit the program.
    Version:
    2018-12-05
    Author:
    Tim Weaver
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      (package private) class  MesonetFrame.BottomPanel
      Bottom Panel class creates the calculate and exit buttons and displays the calculations on the table based on what check boxes are selected.
      (package private) class  MesonetFrame.TopBarFileMenu
      File Menu class creates the top bar with the file menu and has an open file option as well as an exit option.
